text: Sully is a commune in the Saône-et-Loire department in the region of Bourgogne in eastern France. ==People== It was the birthplace of the President Patrice de MacMahon.Encyclopædia Britannica ==See also== *Château de Sully *Communes of the Saône-et-Loire department ==References== *INSEE Category:Communes of Saône-et-Loire
